#### Complex Search [POST]

ELS [Request Body Search](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-request-body.html)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            X-Store-ID: 100

    + Body

            {
              "query": {
                "bool": {
                  "must": {
                    "multi_match": {
                      "query": "tshirt",
                      "fields": [
                        "name",
                        "keywords"
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  "filter": [
                    {
                      "term": {
                        "visible": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              "sort": [
                {
                  "available": {
                    "order": "desc"
                  }
                },
                "_score",
                {
                  "ad_relevance": {
                    "order": "desc"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "views": {
                    "order": "desc"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }

